                "email":"ZexinYan@mail2.sysu.edu.cn"
            }, {
                "username":"Jarvis"
                "password":"jpass"
                "email":"Jarvis@mail2.sysu.edu.cn"
            }
        ]

### User Log Out [POST]

To log out and the token will be removed.

+ Response 204

### Delete a User [DELETE]

To delete the user account from database.

+ Response 204
